responses.title: Hahaha. First Blood is a knight's great honor!

name: Stunning a Teleporting Hero with Storm Hammer

responses.title: Bury me in the Shadeshore ruins.
You should not have crossed me.
You call yourself a knight? Huh.
I guess they let just anyone be a knight these days.
What kind of knight are you?
What you call righteousness, I call foolishness.
Curse you and the horse you rode in on.
Did you think your wings would save you?
That one gives me such a headache.
Gods were meant to be defied.
I've had enough of your bounding!
I would not kill a maiden, but you force the issue.
I have no regard for a knight who follows blindly.
Next time, consider your honor, Omniknight.
You were not up to code, Omniknight.
Dragon or Knight. Make up your mind.
There's enough chaos in this world already.
I have cast you into hell, Chen. Doubt it not.
You should have stood and fought like a man, even if you're not one.
Buy back your own hide now
Had I a face like yours, I too would wear such a mask.
I regret it came to this.

name: Killing Nature's Prophet with Storm Bolt

responses.title: It is an honor to fight beside you.
Huh, what kind of knight are you?
Hm...now what did we learn from this?
By my lights, I can do better!
May my enemies share the fate of the Shattered Helm.
Bitter the orphan's journey--and lonely the orphan's grave.
I owe nothing to codex or covenant.
From a lowly birth in the Shadeshore ruins, who could ever guess I would fight among Heroes?
I will crush my foe as I crushed the Vigil Knights.
One man...in a world of foes...
It's Rogue Knight, dammit! It's not rouge knight.
It's Rogue Knight, it's not rouge knight. Dammit!
This was always meant for me.
I will put you to good use.
The best use for hard-won gold.
Why should I have to pay for what is mine?
Blade in one hand, Scepter in the other.
An offhand complement to my blade.
Daedalus! This is going to be absurd.
There is only one Rogue Knight.
I will be the last thing you never see.
The power of healing fills me.
I swore I would not die unavenged.
I should have done it alone.
You would have lost without me!

responses.title: I'm going to count to one... ONE!
